AlsaMixer.app (dockapp mixer utility)

AlsaMixer.app is a mixer utility for Linux systems using ALSA.  
It is designed to be docked in Window Maker (and other WMs).

This utility has three volume controllers that can be configured 
to handle any sound source. Sound sources can be easily muted,
and there is also wheel mouse support.

Note: the executable is installed as /usr/bin/AlsaMixer, not to
be confused with Slackware's /usr/bin/alsamixer.
